title: Seven examples of lithographic prints
description:
.1 - image of tree with tall grasses in foreground and dark sky in background on thin paper
.2-image of tree with tall grass in foreground and sky in background on thin paper
.3 image of tree with tall grass in foreground and dark sky in background on thin paper; edge of paper is deckled at bottom
.4 - same as .3
.5 - image same as .1-.4 but initials [TP] at LL and [PB] at LR; paper heavier than .1 - .4
[.1 - .5 - word \'lithography\' at bottom]
.6 - image of tree with tall grasses; Maker; Phillip Barber
[PB] at edge of print
.7 - image of tree with tall grasses - very similar to .6 but no initials
[.6 and .7 are matted]
